query:
INSERT INTO github_connections (id, team_id, access_token)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         team_id as "team_id: Uuid",
                         access_token,
                         github_username,
                         connected_at as "connected_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
